{"tid":825421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭得罪左TVB?","createTime":"2018-09-17T14:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T16:02:50.000Z","uid":56147,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"310036274cb0570bcd414529be02adc48dec67ee","tid":825421,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:19:42.000Z","msg":"加一段黎屌林鄭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D16iHCQxefg#t=1m30s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD16iHCQxefg%23t%3D1m30s&d=BA7AskRBlxl8GurbDDSnvMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e129aab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D16iHCQxefg#t=1m30s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180710/58423761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180710%2F58423761&d=BA7AskRBlxl8GurbDDSnvMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8f616975\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180710%2F58423761&h=d1f00a86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180710/58423761</a>"},{"pid":"b6c93001305a519af4ed542bfcdfd1c99a539116","tid":825421,"uid":155818,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"啊爺借TVB把口屌鳩啊娥"},{"pid":"a4932e7e844ff0371b407d1ed9f03185cb08db4a","tid":825421,"uid":29497,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"陳生救屋都不忙自拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea7f8198864a2e0f53c0053e4f7cdc5d9e9b7c8","tid":825421,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"東張西望冇fake 聞部咁奶政府"},{"pid":"1bbb9d0f092f7982eb96b2a7212ed2ed2ec96859","tid":825421,"uid":31002,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"今年7.1對特首林鄭嚟講，梗係大日子啦，皆因係佢上台一周年，又係大騷政績嘅時候。今日佢就喺7.1酒會後同部份傳媒會晤，唔少傳媒都係由高層出席，認真畀面哩，咁林鄭都有來有往，席間又放咗一啲有關房屋土地新方向嘅料，等大家滿載而歸，但可能無綫嘅袁志偉未必咁happy。因為有在席人士報料，話林鄭席間點名TVB袁志偉，話佢哋有個報道出錯，叫佢改改，現場即時傳來一陣竊笑。<br />\n<br />\n探子回報，林鄭當時講緊置業階梯時，突然講咗句：「By the way，呀袁志偉呀吓，你TVB就報道錯誤。」林鄭仲好仔細咁解釋出錯嘅點，話TVB報道首置盤數量縮水得返400個，但其實唔係縮水，而係因為安達臣要3、4年後先可以賣，而額外加多400個，今年底賣咗先呀，據知林鄭仲即場叫袁志偉「唔該修正一下喇」。<br />\n<br />\n聽到袁志偉「被指正」，有指現場即時傳來一陣竊笑，仲有人爆料，話見到袁志偉即時面燶燶咁添。呢件事都證明，林鄭真係睇得傳媒好緊好緊，特別係大台，真係要醒醒定定喇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd1670494b3825e8669bdce8d938a33d6cfaafa","tid":825421,"uid":47042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"晚間新聞狅屌林鄭<br />\n<br />\n播埋大叔大叫 「市民受難日」"},{"pid":"2db650af3d4beb3d1f484b89cfc31f67a29c963c","tid":825421,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"政府廣告落得唔夠多"},{"pid":"67b7ff4763ec9d1963677b4995349bf78e4b1103","tid":825421,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"根本林鄭今日就係人見人憎"},{"pid":"99ef19191c7df13f535be160610ea89c6405af90","tid":825421,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"cctvb想幫689復辟"},{"pid":"789715aee2a21c2349f2d8b